//Show/Hide Results By State Menu
//------------------------------------------
var stateNav = $('.global-election-nav .state-nav');
var stateNavToggle = $('.global-election-nav .state-nav h3 a');
var stateNavMenu = $('.global-election-nav .state-nav-menu');
//Hide menu when clicking anywhere within the HTML element
generalElectionHTML.click(function() {
if (stateNav.is('.state-nav-revealed')) {
stateNav.removeClass('state-nav-revealed');
}
});
//Prevents menu from hiding when interacting with it by stopping the function from bubbling up
stateNavMenu.click(function(event){
event.stopPropagation();
});
//Show or hide the menu when clicking on the toggle elements and disable the link behavior
stateNavToggle.click(function(){
$(this).closest(stateNav).toggleClass("state-nav-revealed");
return false;
});
//------------------------------------------
//Show/Hide Detailed Descriptions
//------------------------------------------
var detailedDescription = $('.detailed-description');
var detailedDescriptionToggle = $('.detailed-description .detailed-description-toggle');
var detailedDescriptionContent = $('.detailed-description .detailed-description-content');
//Hide info box when clicking anywhere within the HTML element
generalElectionHTML.click(function() {
if (detailedDescription.is('.detailed-description-revealed')) {
detailedDescription.removeClass('detailed-description-revealed');
}
});
//Prevents description box from hiding when interacting with it by stopping the function from bubbling up
detailedDescriptionContent.click(function(event){
event.stopPropagation();
});
//Show or hide the description box when clicking on the toggle elements and disable the link behavior
detailedDescriptionToggle.click(function(){
if ($(this).closest(detailedDescription).is('.detailed-description-revealed')) {
$(this).closest(detailedDescription).removeClass('detailed-description-revealed');
} else {
detailedDescription.removeClass('detailed-description-revealed'); //closes any other open boxes
$(this).closest(detailedDescription).addClass('detailed-description-revealed');
}
return false;
});
});
